{"categories":["news-blog-and-magazines","others","travel-leisure","halloween","media-entertainment","holiday"],"collections":"","description":"Immerse in the thrilling spirit of Halloween with our captivating email template. Perfect for News, Blog & Magazines, Media & Entertainment, and Travel platforms, this template is designed to enchant with its dark and mysterious animation. The contrasting hues of black, blue, and red create an eerie atmosphere that is quintessential for a Halloween party invite. Discover the chilling details of the event through the template's captivating LED effects. Make your Halloween event the talk of the town and encourage your guests to get tickets with this engaging template. Ideal for promoting Halloween parties, holiday events, and more, this email template brings your message to life in a truly spine-chilling way.","short_description":"Immerse in the Halloween spirit with our captivating email template, perfect for News, Blog & Magazines, Media & Entertainment, and Travel platforms. Discover the event details with the dark animation, contrasting hues of black, blue, and red, and LED effects. Promote your Halloween party effectively and encourage guests to get tickets with this engaging template.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/matteo-della-chiesa.jpg","description":"I've started to use Photoshop when I was 13. From 2009 to 2014, I've been a part of 5 Art Groups, doing Illustrations and Photo-manipulations, collaborating with over 150 Artists from all the Planet. In 2014, during my final school's exams, I've got my first Freelance Job at a Milan based Agency. Thanks to that first project, I started my Career as a Freelance Independent UI & Web Designer. Today, I help brands improve their online and digital presence, building usable, unique & beautiful products, mostly collaborating with Italian & US Agencies and Startups.","short_description":"","display_name":"Matteo Della Chiesa","id":"ma